{"tid":1781031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 灣仔和你lunch無人知？？","createTime":"2019-12-13T00:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T06:24:01.000Z","uid":284752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd4bfa12bae71ebfa304730542d085098c8d7c2","tid":1781031,"uid":284752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"From tg channel<br />\n<br />\n呢期有唔少人總結返呢半年發生過嘅事，每一個畫面都歷歷在目。 <br />\n<br />\n有冇人會一樣忍唔住睇到喊？？？ <br />\n<br />\n2019年，相信大家都過得不容易，失望，灰心，沮喪，憤怒，我諗大家都有同感。但係我都懇請大家千祈唔好放棄！<br />\n<br />\n羅馬非一日建成，我哋真係要同呢個極權鬥長命！<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可 <br />\n#憑良知不顧一切盡做<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n灣仔和你lunch <br />\nLunch with you in Wan Chai<br />\n<br />\n日期 Date : 13/12/2019 星期五 Friday <br />\n時間 Time : 1pm<br />\n地點 Venue : 灣仔稅務大樓 The Revenue Tower，Wan Chai<br />\n<br />\n係灣仔做咗咁多年野，從來未試過野餐！一於約大家今個星期五一齊食生命麵包！<br />\n<br />\n除咗生命麵包之外，大家可以考慮帶以下嘅嘢：<br />\n<br />\n1.  口罩 (呢排多人病，袋番個穩陣啲）<br />\n<br />\n2. 長遮（有機會落雨喎）<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果你本身既工作崗位比較敏感，麻煩大家包密實啲自己呀🙆🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n4. 蒸餾水<br />\n<br />\n5. 文宣/旗/pepe/ memo 紙/筆/ 膠紙 ... ...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀各位12.13一齊食通灣仔‼️<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/lunchwithme_wanchai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flunchwithme_wanchai&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=018814d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lunchwithme_wanchai</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️嚴正聲明⚠️<br />\n<br />\n本channel 同中環和你lunch 係冇任何關係！之前因為豬隊友admin A太懶，直出佢地個post 而引起大家嘅誤會，眾admins 全體致歉🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12.07 00:21 補充：<br />\n<br />\n另外，都有人會認為點解灣仔要分開搞？ 其實因為好多打工仔食飯都係得一個鐘，係唔搭黨鐵既情況下，有好多灣仔友都未必會join 到😞<br />\n<br />\n截至目前為止，參與人數都係太太太太少😞😞😞 <br />\n我哋會繼續努力，希望有更加多人知！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDS1GDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDS1GDZ.jpg&h=c615a02a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96700014501b2bbda224a9f502aabcb09f897ba6","tid":1781031,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T00:55:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">世界戰綫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發動世界級遊行！Who stand with us世界巡遊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d810b75a181438d41feb995f67e080a185e7ef2","tid":1781031,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"行動post 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bbc2ae4127c0b84712245c7fb1ec1f30d96a38","tid":1781031,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd2ab6e4710e908c5cfbfe734365784df3cf0b3","tid":1781031,"uid":256393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"冇人？"},{"pid":"c4fe2b0c65e6bd82138f96b44abf3eb9751e4031","tid":1781031,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"296fc7304c1cc11d696eefa51efe4a20f96a6133","tid":1781031,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c08c7579d1413334d314b6e4139b9110cde04369","tid":1781031,"uid":120805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"去咗，應該都有接近200人"}]}